<item>
  <title>ASSISTANT PROGRAMME DIRECTOR-PAEDIATRICS &amp; ADOLESCENT HEALTH(CONTRACT POSITION)</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/assistant-programme-director-paediatrics-adolescent-healthcontract-position</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;ASSISTANT PROGRAMME DIRECTOR-PAEDIATRICS &amp; ADOLESCENT HEALTH(CONTRACT POSITION)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;ramahobok&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Wed, 07/12/2022 - 09:54&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Paediatrics and Adolescent Health&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;FACULTY OF MEDICINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF PAEDIATRICS &amp; ADOLESCENT HEALTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ASSISTANT PROGRAMME DIRECTOR (CONTRACT POSITION)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY NO: FM/DPAH02/2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The University of Botswana (&lt;strong&gt;www.ub.bw&lt;/strong&gt;) is the largest and most prestigious institution of higher learning in the country. It has opened the country’s first Faculty of Medicine and is affiliated to an adjacent new state-of-art 450-bed, the Sir Ketumile Masire Teaching Hospital. The first MBBS undergraduate intake was in August 2009. Undergraduate medical training is by a Problem Based Learning [PBL] Hybrid approach, which is integrated and community oriented. The Faculty of Medicine runs a number of Masters of Medicine (MMed) (residency) programmes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;he successful applicant will be required to; &lt;strong&gt;(i)&lt;/strong&gt; assist the Head of the Department (HOD) in implementing the education of undergraduate and postgraduate students and of medical interns, junior doctors and other members of the clinical care team in the clinical teaching facilities; &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; provide patient care and training in the area of Paediatrics and Adolescent Health; &lt;strong&gt;(iii)&lt;/strong&gt; participate in relevant research;  &lt;strong&gt;(iv)&lt;/strong&gt; work with the Dean of the Faculty of Medicine, health facilities clinical staff (Ministry of Health), HOD and hospital leadership to set priorities in education, research, service, recruitment and infrastructure enhancement; &lt;strong&gt;(v)&lt;/strong&gt; assist the HOD to monitor and evaluate the effectiveness of academic programmes; &lt;strong&gt;(vi)&lt;/strong&gt; act for the HOD as may be required and perform any other duties as may be assigned by the HOD.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;: applicant should have; &lt;strong&gt;(i)&lt;/strong&gt; at least a Bachelor of Medicine/Bachelor of Surgery or other recognised medical qualification (MD); &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; a specialist qualification in General Paediatrics or relevant Paediatric sub-speciality with a minimum of &lt;strong&gt;5&lt;/strong&gt; years of post-specialisation experience in professional practice.  Candidates with less than 5 years post-specialisation experience may be considered under special circumstances. The qualification must be registerable by the Botswana Health Professions Council with a specialist status; &lt;strong&gt;(iii)&lt;/strong&gt; must have been a Lecturer (preferably Senior Lecturer) in the preceding 12 months prior to appointment; &lt;strong&gt;(iv)&lt;/strong&gt; at least 1 year of distinctive record of leadership and administration of university level institution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Attributes and skills required:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(i)&lt;/strong&gt; excellent communication and organisational skills; &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; strong academic leadership skills and sympathy for the values and culture of the University; &lt;strong&gt;(iii)&lt;/strong&gt; good management, human relations, sound analytical and coordinating skills.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duration of the contract: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;the above position is available for a restricted-term contract&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt; of three years and may be renewed for a further term of three years on the basis of satisfactory performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Remuneration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt; the University offers competitive salaries and benefits commensurate with qualifications and experience. For information on the University, please visit our website;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.ub.bw"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;www.ub.bw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;How to apply:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt; applicants should address the stated qualification and provide any other information to assist the University determine their suitability for the position.  They should quote the vacancy number of the post applied for, provide current CVs (including telephone, skype and email address), certified true copies of educational certificates, transcripts, samples of the relevant publications, and names, addresses and contact details of three referees  and address these to: &lt;strong&gt;The Human Resources Manager, Faculty of Medicine, Corner of Notwane and Mabuto Road, University of Botswana, Private Bag 00713 Gaborone, Botswana; or Email: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:tshoganetsom@UB.AC.BW"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;tshoganetsom@UB.AC.BW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;Applicants &lt;span&gt;should inform their referees to&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;(i)&lt;/strong&gt; quote the vacancy number; &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; position applied for, and; &lt;strong&gt;(iii)&lt;/strong&gt; submit the references directly to the address stated above before the stipulated closing date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hand delivered applications should be sent &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;to:  &lt;strong&gt;Faculty &lt;span&gt;of Medicine, Sir Ketumile Masire Teaching Hospital (SKMTH), 3rd Floor, Office F4003 or F4004.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note that applications with incomplete information shall not be acknowledged.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NB:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date:  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Open until filled.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

